com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud

Class KontaktCloudImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.KontaktCloudImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KontaktCloud

    public class KontaktCloudImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements KontaktCloud
    Kontakt.io Proximity REST API client implementation. To obtain Kontakt Cloud instance please use KontaktCloudFactory.create(String) or KontaktCloudFactory.create() method, for example: 
       
   KontaktCloud kontaktCloud = KontaktCloudFactory.create();
   KontaktCloud kontaktCloud = KontaktCloudFactory.create("my-api-key");
